<topic id="kindle-transformation-output">
  <title>DITA Map Kindle Transformation</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Transformation Scenarios<indexterm>DITA Map to Kindle</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>DITA Map to Kindle transformation </indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_nbl_cgk_54b"><ph keyref="product"/> requires <term>KindleGen</term> to generate Kindle output from <xref
        keyref="glossentry_ditamap"><term>DITA maps</term></xref>. To install <term>KindleGen</term>
      for use by <ph keyref="product"/>, follow these steps:<ol id="ol_obl_cgk_54b">
        <li id="li_pbl_cgk_54b">Go to <xref href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/feature.html/?docId=1000765211" format="html"
            scope="external">www.amazon.com/kindleformat/kindlegen</xref> and download the zip file
          that matches your operating system.</li>
        <li id="li_qbl_cgk_54b">Unzip the file on your local disk.</li>
        <li id="li_rbl_cgk_54b">Start <ph keyref="product"/> and open a <term>DITA map</term><ph
            product="author editor authorEclipse editorEclipse"> in the <xref
              href="dita-maps-manager.dita#dita-maps-manager"><uicontrol>DITA Maps
                Manager</uicontrol> view</xref></ph>.</li>
        <li id="li_sbl_cgk_54b">Click the <uicontrol><image id="image_d3c_lxq_vr" href="../img/TransformConfig16.png"
            />Configure Transformation Scenario(s)</uicontrol> button.</li>
        <li id="li_tbl_cgk_54b">Select the <uicontrol>DITA Map Kindle</uicontrol> transformation and click the
            <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol> button to edit it. </li>
        <li id="li_ubl_cgk_54b">Go to <uicontrol>Parameters</uicontrol> tab and set the
            <uicontrol>kindlegen.executable</uicontrol> parameter as the path to the
            <i>KindleGen</i> directory.</li>
        <li id="li_vbl_cgk_54b">Accept the changes. </li>
      </ol></p>
  </body>
</topic>
